    "body": "<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\nchefs mom has collection of <b>N</b> chocolates. Each chocolate has different taste value. Mom has some rules, \nchef can eat atmost 3 chocolates in a row, to eat next chocolates he must skip atleast 1 chocolate.<br>\nChef wants to get maximum possible taste value.<br>\nFind out maximum possible taste value chef can get. \n</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p>First line of input contains <b>T</b> , the number of test cases <br>\nFirst line of each test case contains <b>N</b> the number of elements.<br>Second line of each test case contains <b>N</b> elements separated by space denoting the taste value</p>\n\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p> Print maximum possible taste value</p>\n\n<h3>Constraints</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>T</b> \u2264 <b>100</b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>N</b> \u2264 <b>2*10^4</b></li>\n<li><b>1</b> \u2264 <b>Taste Value</b> \u2264 <b>10^5</b></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<pre><b>Input:</b>\n1\n6\n4 2 8 5 1 4\n\n<b>Output:</b>\n21\n\n<h3>Explaination</h3>\n<b>sample case 1:</b><p>chef can select chocolate at 1,3,4 & 6 (1-base indexing) to get maximum taste value.</p>",
